President Trump
and the administration calls
into question

20:58.691 --> 21:04.463 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
the integrity of the elections,
they're simply
setting the stage for proposed
changes to

21:04.497 --> 21:09.335 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
policy and changes to law that
will follow
that will take our country
backwards as it

21:09.368 --> 21:11.203 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
pertains to voting rights.

21:11.237 --> 21:13.038 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And we need to push back every
step of the
way.

21:13.072 --> 21:17.376 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
WILLIAM BRANGHAM: Mr. Padilla,
though, staying
with you, a lot of conservatives
will argue

21:17.409 --> 21:22.381 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
that if you don't need to have
an I.D. to
prove you are who you say you
are when you

21:22.414 --> 21:27.253 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
