widespread voter
fraud, and you just wouldn't
know about it?

21:27.286 --> 21:32.691 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
ALEX PADILLA: There's a lot of
hypotheticals
that people would like to kind
of put out

21:32.725 --> 21:36.395 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
