create the
doubt.

21:36.428 --> 21:39.865 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
But the fact of the matter is,
voter fraud
isn't something that we just
started paying

21:39.899 --> 21:42.168 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
attention to in this November
election.

21:42.201 --> 21:45.871 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
