in each and
every election cycle.

21:45.905 --> 21:51.844 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And there has been study after
study, report
after report, investigation
after investigation

21:51.877 --> 21:55.414 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
