not canceled.

23:16.362 --> 23:21.700 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
But we have very little evidence
of people
engaging in -- certainly in
impersonation

23:21.734 --> 23:25.971 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
fraud, which you mentioned
earlier, double
