29:17.456 --> 29:21.293 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
So, just it kind of depends on a
case-by-case
basis, but there is no question
that there

29:21.326 --> 29:24.496 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
